title: Rare Hits of The 80s Vol. 15
description:
Rare Hits of The 80s Vol. 15. Another compilation of rare and obscure 80s stuff. This might be the last of these series I upload. By uploading these I just wanted to demonstrate to some people that 80s did not mean only Madonna or Wham and that there&#039;s tons of cool obscure 80s stuff out there for you to discover! enjoy......
